data.description: Ask about seller concessions available to help with interest rate buy-down and closing costs!!! This home is move-in ready with 3 beds/2.5 baths and it has its own backyard paradise with a screened patio and large shed for storage. Beautiful vinyl flooring, fresh paint throughout, approximately 2 year old roof and radiant barrier are just a few upgrades to name. This home offers an abundance of natural light with high quality Pella windows installed 3 years ago. Have a large family or need room to spread out? No problem. The office, 2 living rooms and extra closets give plenty of space for storage. Meadows of Morningside is a highly desired neighborhood with schools close by and plenty to do for your family. You will find several playgrounds, a splash pad and walking and biking trails within a short distance of the home. Located in an area with easy access to IH-35 in New Braunfels and close to San Antonio. Schedule a showing today!
